data.description: NEW PRICE!! Come look at this charming home conveniently located in Calhoun. The split floorplan has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, vaulted ceilings & stained concrete floors. All kitchen appliances remain, there is a large pantry & separate dining area. The master bedroom is spacious with a decorative tray ceiling. The attached on suite bathroom has separate tub and shower, double sinks & a great walk in closet. A new roof was installed in October. Enjoy your evenings sitting on the 24X24 deck overlooking the pond. Call your favorite Realtor to set up your showing today!
